metadata.name: Feel Good
metadata.description:
This new collaborative project is a feel good moment suspended in time with a touch of lo-fi background music. Visual artist Regards Coupables and music producer Roman Kouder, both based in Paris, have already worked on a 8 tracks length album titled "REAL", released in 2021 and available on all streaming platforms.
MP4/25FPS/1080x1920px

About Roman Kouder
Roman Kouder is a Universal Music signed artist who released electronic productions for more than 5 years and counts millions of streams all around the world.
RK also produced for other artists like Mosimann or Ana Majidson, podcasts, original TV productions (Netflix, France TV, PrimeVideo) and DJ for radio (Radio FG, BBC).
